G. J. Ikenberry, "A World Economy Restored: Expert Concensus and the Anglo-American
Postwar Settlement", International Organization, vol. 46 (1992): 289-321. 

Jeffry A. Frieden, "Invested Interests: The Politics of National Economic
Policies in a World of Global Finance," International Organization, vol.
45, no. 4 (1991). 

April 13  The Politics of International Trade  


RG, ch. 5. 

SH, ch. 3. 

CA, pp. 245-262. 

