International Affairs, vol. 72 (1996), pp. 227-246. 

Benjamin J. Cohen, "The Political Economy of International Trade," International
Organization, vol. 44, no. 2 (1990), pp. 261-281. 

April 20  Transnational Production and Multinational Corporations 


SH, chs. 4 & 8. 

RG, ch. 6. 

