Markusen, James R., "The boundaries of multinational enterprises and the
theory of international trade,"Journal of Economic Perspectives, vol. 9,
no. 2, (1995), pp. 169-189. 

April 27 The Political Economy of International Finance 


RG, ch. 8. 

SH, ch. 6. 

